                <div><span>取鏡片並在當日開始使用</span></div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div><span>STEP 4</span></div>
                <div>
                  <span>覆診：配戴後一星期及</span
                  ><span>每３個月接受視光檢查</span><span>及量度眼軸</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

